	FREENECT_VIDEO_IR_10BIT_SIZE FREENECT_VIDEO_IR_8BIT
	FREENECT_VIDEO_IR_8BIT_SIZE FREENECT_VIDEO_RGB FREENECT_VIDEO_RGB_SIZE
